YOUTUBE DATA NOTICE

This project uses the YouTube Data API v3 and displays channel avatar images
and stream thumbnails served from YouTube's CDN (yt3.ggpht.com,
i.ytimg.com). Such data and media are used under the YouTube API Terms of
Service (https://developers.google.com/youtube/terms/api-services-terms-of-service)
and remain the property of their respective channel owners. This project is
non-commercial and uses them solely as an analytics reference. Nothing in
this license grants any rights to that data or media.
